CSC462 project description

We would like to create a 3D environment, including a Townhouse, a waterfall, a mountain, and a lake.
We would include a fireworks effects. Inside the house, we will set up furniture as a real world house does. 
A camera can go (up, down, left, right), and rotate the view( look up, look down, look right, look left). 
We choose unity 3D as implementation platform. C# language as program language. The effects contains: 
Occlusion culling, Global Illumination, Reflection, Bump mapping, Flock and particles, Terrain rendering, Fluid and goo, Animation. \

